@subsection{Equality}

@deftogether[(
@defthing[equal? ('a 'a -> boolean)]
)]{

Compares two values for equality. Roughly, two values are
@racket[equal?] when they print the same, but opaque values such as
functions are @racket[equal?] only if they are @racket[eq?].

@examples[#:eval demo
